6920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:08:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a66b86bb9e54de9f526cfc910d145b295e97d07a","tid":1760020,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:09:07.000Z","msg":"推推推 做人要知恩圖報<br />\n<br />\n感恩節推爆佢"},{"pid":"aded21368ffcd40e2ac91d50846d6bd638abde56","tid":1760020,"uid":85822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"借個位宣傳吸引火力黎推post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfor 想體力升級/心態提升為民請命手足參考<br />\n補師我要幫全世界身心升level<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入黎補補正能量整理下個人狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人夠正能量先頂到落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各做所長<br />\n若要勝利 必須備戰<br />\n營養＋運動 身心感覺同樣重要<br />\n<br />\n極權將破 在支爆前會係最黑暗嘅時候<br />\n幾艱難 損失都要打落去<br />\n<br />\n和理勇武強身強心飲食入門：<br />\n全世界維持健康打落去<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人人都要有自衞隊身體質素<br />\n香港人 團結反抗 無退路<br />\n未來嘅希望由我地做起<br />\n<br />\nStep 8.心理健康 正能量撚❤️<br />\n當我地遇到情況📍 在安全情況下<br />\n⚡️減少重複接觸影響自己的負面人事<br />\n🍎做自己鍾意的事<br />\n😀約定 定期運動放鬆 <br />\n🧠睇書/聽Motivation Video<br />\n🔥最緊要痴住正能量嘅朋友/人<br />\n<br />\n利申：健康教練<br />\nHerbalife  健康教練<br />\n唔係重點 重點係大家要長命幫手贏<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民皆兵</span></span> <br />\n依家風頭火勢 好多五毛<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 團結 正能量<br />\n呢個世界唔係我地影響人<br />\n就係人地影響緊我地<br />\n我地要內在夠強 百毒不侵<br />\n<br />\n永續健康身心 長期抗爭致勝<br />\n有咩搵我幫手 免費教大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港需要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有需TG 唔問名 <br />\n幫你Case Study <br />\n教你點飲食點運動打仗飲食法<br />\n20％運動 80％營養<br />\n學完再善用Budget 搞好自己體能<br />\n得閒係屋企做下運動放鬆<br />\n行一陣街吸哂TG 暈低仲點打落去<br />\n<br />\nMy TG<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTreeHoIsGood&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtONdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=1e828a7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood</a><br />\nChannel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FtreehoHealthAdvice&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtONdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=c837f876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice</a><br />\n討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/THHATalk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTHHATalk&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtONdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=dfb5510b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/THHATalk</a><br />\n長期戰爭 齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對抗白色恐怖 <br />\n反共抗中 我地勢不兩立<br />\nWe Shall Never Surrender<br />\n<br />\nUnited, We can win the fight"},{"pid":"d2606a56253bcabb3a86a5bf16be6fec2e88b279","tid":1760020,"uid":11450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e073c397fee8f6764a94e25394b1cc47a15b62","tid":1760020,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:11:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f012d6fb4e6601d63155c41fa65b580cf00a20","tid":1760020,"uid":113516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:12:55.000Z","msg":"手足要知恩圖報!!!!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快d 上twitter 講thank you 同retweet呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde87b78b077f141b54d0ed8f6cb50b7993f8319","tid":1760020,"uid":105353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:17:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e63a918f2b6201e4ed7ed760493